Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.28,0:01:50.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Off it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:58.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he and golf mix well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:02:03.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he says he's not good at any sports that use equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:06.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he should've said no...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:08.90,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The reason he picked up golf
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:13.44,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}was a phone call from Nichiuri TV three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:17.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Pro-amateur charity golf tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:20.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but golf's not really my—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:23.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Yoko Okino recommended me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:25.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoko-{\i1}chan{\i0}'s entering?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:28.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it! I may not look like it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:32.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm actually a golf master!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:35.92,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:41.26,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}...just because early morning is cheaper,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:43.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}6:30 is {\i1}too{\i0} early!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:46.43,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Especially when you're dragging us along!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:51.88,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)\pos(320,310)}Itsui Electronics\NDirector of Product Development\NEisuke Tachibana (56)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:51.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then! Let's work up another good sweat today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:55.84,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(320,310)}Itsui Electronics\NProduct Development Manager\NMinoru Yasui (44)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:55.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's perfect exercise just before work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:59.80,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,310)}Itsui Electronics\NProduct Development Chief\NTatsuya Okubo (35)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:59.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, my health's gotten much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:02.76,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,310)}Itsui Electronics\NProduct Development Employee\NTomofumi Minami (28)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:02.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I bet so!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:06.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10\pos(320,240)\3c&HFFEEEE&\c&HFFEEEE&\bord300\clip(m 554 241 l 211 222 222 133 563 149 554 241)}.
